descriptionHtml:
The Fallen were created by the Aedra and known as the Divine . They were holy immortals who ranked highest of the Aedra\'s servants. After aeons of battling the Daedra the Divine developed a taste for slaughter and cruelty. Their very beings were twisted by the evil that festered in their souls, changing them from holy servants of light into evil demonic beings. They were stripped of their divine power, cast down to Mundus and were henceforth known as the Fallen.

SKILLS

Heavy Armor 10
One Handed 5
Smithing 5
Destruction 5
Restoration 5
Lockpicking 5

POWERS/ABILITIES

Enslave Soul
Demonic Terror
10% Resistance to magic


Dark Elf Voice type Optional ESP uploaded (If you dont like the dremora voice)
